WEBVTT



00:00:11.439 --> 00:00:12.199
Captain

00:00:12.399 --> 00:00:13.319
This Boss Hu

00:00:13.359 --> 00:00:15.479
He's been buying from Lao Zhao for years

00:00:15.479 --> 00:00:16.600
Could he possibly know

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:18.000
something we don't know?

00:00:18.399 --> 00:00:20.000
And Lao Zhao alone

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.399
couldn't easily kill and dump his wife

00:00:22.399 --> 00:00:23.239
This Boss Hu

00:00:23.239 --> 00:00:24.200
might've been involved too

00:00:24.959 --> 00:00:25.559
Boss Hu

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:26.239
Yes

00:00:26.280 --> 00:00:26.840
Where's the evidence?

00:00:28.799 --> 00:00:29.600
I don't have any yet

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:30.600
but I can look into it

00:00:30.879 --> 00:00:31.399
Lin Shen

00:00:32.439 --> 00:00:33.840
Lately, working cases

00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:35.200
have you been a bit impatient?

00:00:40.919 --> 00:00:41.439
Yes

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:42.159
Zhi Yuan

00:00:42.240 --> 00:00:43.159
Meet at the usual place

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:43.799
Okay

00:00:45.759 --> 00:00:46.520
I'm stepping out for a bit

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:47.840
Carry on with the meeting.

00:01:18.319 --> 00:01:20.000
You ordered so much, can you finish it?

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:21.680
I didn't eat lunch

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:22.239
I'm hungry

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:24.559
Boss

00:01:25.239 --> 00:01:27.440
Your shop's in a pretty good spot

00:01:27.959 --> 00:01:29.839
The foot traffic is high and steady

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:30.919
And it's quite visible.

00:01:30.959 --> 00:01:31.519
Right?

00:01:31.879 --> 00:01:32.440
Why?

00:01:32.639 --> 00:01:33.919
Interested in doing business?

00:01:35.319 --> 00:01:37.480
A relative wants to start a business.

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:38.720
So they asked me to look into it.

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:44.400
You're left-handed, huh

00:01:45.120 --> 00:01:46.480
You cut meat every day

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:48.639
That left hand must be really strong

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:50.000
Bigger than the right

00:02:07.239 --> 00:02:07.720
Boss Hu

00:02:07.720 --> 00:02:09.800
The person in this painting looks like you

00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:10.279
Me

00:02:10.440 --> 00:02:10.960
I...

00:02:12.320 --> 00:02:14.279
So this painting was

00:02:14.759 --> 00:02:15.639
painted by you?

00:02:16.119 --> 00:02:17.039
Just a little hobby

00:02:17.080 --> 00:02:17.839
Just doodling

00:02:19.479 --> 00:02:21.399
You have a real talent for art, then.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:25.000
Sorry about that

00:02:27.919 --> 00:02:29.279
Some things from when I was a kid

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:31.080
That explains it

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:33.199
There's quite a hidden space in there.

00:02:33.960 --> 00:02:35.039
I'll show you.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:36.759
No need

00:02:37.639 --> 00:02:38.240
No

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:38.960
Sorry to offend

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:39.679
Sorry to offend

00:02:39.919 --> 00:02:40.199
It's fine

00:02:40.199 --> 00:02:40.759
Sorry to offend

00:02:40.800 --> 00:02:41.559
Have a seat first

00:02:41.559 --> 00:02:42.360
Go ahead and eat

00:02:42.440 --> 00:02:43.279
It'll be right out

00:03:03.919 --> 00:03:04.639
Here, Lu Yi

00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:05.800
Here

00:03:05.800 --> 00:03:06.880
Hand out the rest

00:03:09.119 --> 00:03:10.800
You all have the autopsy report.

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:11.479
Captain

00:03:12.119 --> 00:03:13.119
I told you, this Boss Hu

00:03:13.119 --> 00:03:13.880
is definitely suspicious.

00:03:13.880 --> 00:03:14.639
Right now in his shop

00:03:14.639 --> 00:03:16.399
there's a creepy self-portrait hanging

00:03:16.399 --> 00:03:18.119
And behind it there's something locked

00:03:18.119 --> 00:03:18.679
Lin Shen

00:03:21.839 --> 00:03:24.479
Even if Boss Hu is suspicious,

00:03:24.479 --> 00:03:26.279
aren't you tipping him off like this?

00:03:26.559 --> 00:03:28.240
This is basic procedure

00:03:29.479 --> 00:03:30.119
Captain, I...

00:03:30.119 --> 00:03:31.080
You what?

00:03:31.880 --> 00:03:32.600
Here's what we'll do

00:03:33.839 --> 00:03:35.240
I've noticed lately

00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:36.479
your emotions have been quite volatile.

00:03:37.119 --> 00:03:37.960
Take some time off

00:03:38.720 --> 00:03:39.320
and clear your head.

00:03:39.479 --> 00:03:40.039
All right?

00:03:40.479 --> 00:03:40.960
Captain

00:03:41.279 --> 00:03:42.320
I'm very calm right now

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:43.839
I suspect recently...

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:52.800
Take some time off.

00:03:57.479 --> 00:03:57.839
Fine

00:03:57.839 --> 00:03:58.360
Captain

00:03:59.679 --> 00:04:00.360
I'll take some time off.

00:04:07.320 --> 00:04:07.880
Back to the meeting.

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:45.200
No, thanks

00:04:56.799 --> 00:04:57.239
You guys...

00:04:57.839 --> 00:04:58.720
I'm telling you

00:04:58.880 --> 00:04:59.399
This...

00:04:59.399 --> 00:05:00.200
She's already gone

00:05:00.200 --> 00:05:01.519
and you still cut her open?

00:05:02.679 --> 00:05:03.279
I'm telling you

00:05:03.279 --> 00:05:04.920
She can't be buried in the family grave

00:05:10.799 --> 00:05:12.160
Just leave her in peace.

00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:14.480
There's nothing to check in our home.

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:15.959
Calm down, calm down

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:17.679
You suspect me, don't you?

00:05:21.799 --> 00:05:24.160
We've been an old married couple for ages

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:33.239
My old woman...

00:05:33.239 --> 00:05:34.679
Your fate...

00:05:39.359 --> 00:05:41.399
is so bitter

00:06:18.440 --> 00:06:18.920
Lin!

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:23.440
Come here, look!

00:06:29.119 --> 00:06:30.399
We found a stick like the murder weapon

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:04.600
Our daughter hasn't been home for so long

00:07:05.959 --> 00:07:06.880
Tell me, how did our

00:07:07.640 --> 00:07:09.119
perfectly good family

00:07:10.760 --> 00:07:12.040
end up like this?

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:30.519
Who are you looking for?

00:07:32.040 --> 00:07:32.880
Hello, ma'am

00:07:33.239 --> 00:07:34.760
I'm Lu Yi's friend

00:07:35.079 --> 00:07:35.920
My name is Lin Shen

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:38.440
Xiao Lu's friend?

00:07:38.799 --> 00:07:39.640
Come in, quick

00:07:39.839 --> 00:07:41.000
Lu Yi's been too busy lately

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:42.359
So I came to visit you.

00:07:43.720 --> 00:07:44.519
Come in

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:45.640
Come, come

00:07:46.079 --> 00:07:47.799
Xiao Lu mentioned you before

00:07:47.959 --> 00:07:49.119
You know, our kid

00:07:49.119 --> 00:07:50.600
to have a friend like you

00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:51.880
is really rare.

00:07:52.679 --> 00:07:53.320
Come, come

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:55.160
I brought some things for you.

00:07:55.160 --> 00:07:56.359
You shouldn't have.

00:07:56.359 --> 00:07:56.839
It's nothing.

00:07:56.839 --> 00:07:58.000
I'll get you some fruit

00:07:58.320 --> 00:07:59.279
Don't trouble yourself, ma'am

00:08:00.119 --> 00:08:00.959
It's fine

00:08:00.959 --> 00:08:01.519
Oh, right

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:04.200
This is what Lu Yi left behind last time.

00:08:04.399 --> 00:08:06.119
Her room is inside, on the right.

00:08:06.119 --> 00:08:07.200
You can go put it in there.

00:08:07.359 --> 00:08:07.799
Okay

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:09.279
Make yourself at home

00:09:18.039 --> 00:09:18.960
Xiao Shen

00:09:19.159 --> 00:09:20.400
Come have some fruit

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:24.080
Coming

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:28.840
Have a seat.

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:29.880
Ma'am

00:09:30.599 --> 00:09:32.559
I'd like to go see Uncle Lu

00:09:33.919 --> 00:09:34.640
Let's go

00:10:00.919 --> 00:10:01.799
Uncle Lu

00:10:03.119 --> 00:10:04.159
My name is Lin Shen

00:10:05.359 --> 00:10:06.200
Wang Hai'an

00:10:07.520 --> 00:10:08.520
is my uncle

00:10:21.599 --> 00:10:22.880
How do you know Morse Code?

00:10:23.039 --> 00:10:24.520
My dad taught me when I was little

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:27.559
My dad said it was our

00:10:28.520 --> 00:10:29.320
father-daughter secret code.

00:10:57.479 --> 00:10:58.479
It was me

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:01.039
It was me

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:04.559
I'll talk.

00:11:07.159 --> 00:11:08.400
That old woman

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:11.520
I was the one who killed her

00:11:12.280 --> 00:11:13.119
That day

00:11:13.599 --> 00:11:14.679
I'd had a bit to drink

00:11:15.840 --> 00:11:17.280
She kept cursing me

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:19.679
Calling me

00:11:20.280 --> 00:11:21.520
the most awful things.

00:11:22.440 --> 00:11:23.919
I just couldn't take it anymore

00:11:24.640 --> 00:11:25.960
In a daze

00:11:26.280 --> 00:11:27.640
I grabbed a stick

00:11:30.400 --> 00:11:31.760
and hit her with it.

00:11:32.799 --> 00:11:33.599
How did you hit her?

00:11:34.400 --> 00:11:35.200
Where did you hit her?

00:11:36.039 --> 00:11:37.200
The victim was struck with a blunt object

00:11:37.200 --> 00:11:38.320
causing a skull fracture

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:39.520
leading to her death.

00:11:42.200 --> 00:11:43.119
I don't remember

00:11:45.039 --> 00:11:45.880
At the time,

00:11:47.679 --> 00:11:48.919
I'd had too much to drink

00:11:51.880 --> 00:11:53.840
I can't remember clearly.

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:57.559
I hit her a few times

00:11:58.320 --> 00:11:59.559
and she was gone.

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:04.280
That night you were drinking,

00:12:05.479 --> 00:12:06.960
were you drinking alone?

00:12:18.119 --> 00:12:19.080
Officer

00:12:20.039 --> 00:12:21.880
I've confessed to everything.

00:12:23.880 --> 00:12:25.200
These old bones of mine

00:12:25.840 --> 00:12:27.760
I've lived long enough anyway

00:12:29.320 --> 00:12:30.840
Just sentence me already.

00:12:37.280 --> 00:12:38.200
Is it Boss Hu?

00:12:41.400 --> 00:12:42.159
Captain Duan wants you

00:12:42.559 --> 00:12:43.599
Someone turned themselves in

00:12:55.679 --> 00:12:57.520
You said you killed Lao Zhao's wife

00:12:58.039 --> 00:12:58.679
Yeah

00:12:59.359 --> 00:13:00.239
I killed her

00:13:00.239 --> 00:13:00.960
Why?

00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:10.280
Okay.

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:12.359
On the day of the crime,

00:13:12.359 --> 00:13:14.080
you were drinking with Lao Zhao

00:13:14.719 --> 00:13:15.400
That's right

00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:18.159
I'd had too much to drink.

00:13:19.039 --> 00:13:19.919
I acted on impulse.

00:13:19.919 --> 00:13:20.640
What made you

00:13:20.640 --> 00:13:21.640
snap and commit murder?

00:13:22.760 --> 00:13:23.880
That woman

00:13:23.880 --> 00:13:24.960
she was such a snob

00:13:24.960 --> 00:13:26.000
She said I jinxed my parents to death,

00:13:26.559 --> 00:13:27.799
and that I'd come to ruin their family

00:13:27.799 --> 00:13:28.320
Borrow money?

00:13:28.320 --> 00:13:29.039
What money do you have?

00:13:29.039 --> 00:13:29.559
Get lost!

00:13:30.239 --> 00:13:31.880
I just wanted to borrow a little money

00:13:32.599 --> 00:13:34.599
Worst of all was her cursing Brother Zhao.

00:13:35.239 --> 00:13:36.640
Brother Zhao is my benefactor

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:38.280
Cursing him is like slapping my face.

00:13:38.400 --> 00:13:39.520
She was asking to die

00:13:44.919 --> 00:13:46.520
I felt deeply humiliated.

00:13:46.799 --> 00:13:47.640
I grabbed a stick

00:13:47.640 --> 00:13:48.640
and beat her to death.

00:13:48.640 --> 00:13:49.520
How did you hit her?

00:13:49.760 --> 00:13:50.599
Where did you hit her?

00:13:50.919 --> 00:13:51.520
Her head

00:13:52.320 --> 00:13:53.479
Over and over

00:14:08.960 --> 00:14:10.640
Just because she insulted you a few times

00:14:10.679 --> 00:14:12.039
you were brutal enough to kill her

00:14:14.520 --> 00:14:15.559
I heard when you were young

00:14:15.559 --> 00:14:17.159
you hung out with Lao Zhao too

00:14:17.159 --> 00:14:18.159
getting drunk every day

00:14:20.960 --> 00:14:22.520
What exactly is your relationship?